                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 859.001F87/6.]</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">King of Denmark</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">President of the United States</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lyngby</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-05-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 16, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I am most grateful for your kind expression of sympathy in the profound grief
                    caused by the death of the King, my deeply lamented father.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Christian R.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
